snippet.title: Mera FIRST LOOK Aquaman 2018 Costume - Beyond Trailer
snippet.description:
Mera First Look in Aquaman 2018! Beyond The Trailer's reaction & review! New costume for Amber Heard! James Wan on Twitter! DCEU!
http://bit.ly/subscribeBTT

Mera First Look today! Beyond The Trailer host Grace Randolph's reaction and review of the new costume for Amber Heard as Mera in Aquaman 2018! Revealed on Twitter by James Wan! More color! Should there be more color in the DCEU? Share your own reaction to the new costume for Mera in Aquaman 2018 vs her Justice League costume before you see each full movie!
